features.title:
Durable Foam Guarantees
Long Lasting Use
features.description: This pouf is crafted with high-density foam that resists sagging and wear, ensuring it retains its shape and support even with daily use. Whether you're sitting, lounging, or using it as a footrest, the durable foam guarantees comfort and longevity, making it a reliable addition to your space.

features.title:
Soft, Carefully Selected
Fabrics
features.description: Wrapped in premium, carefully selected fabrics, this pouf offers a luxurious feel that’s gentle to the touch. The soft texture enhances comfort while adding a sophisticated touch to your space, ensuring a cozy and stylish experience.

features.title: Multi-Purpose Application
features.description: Designed to adapt to your needs, this pouf serves as a comfortable seat, a supportive footrest, or even a stylish accent piece. Its multi-purpose functionality makes it a practical and versatile addition to any room.

specifications.description: Searching for a minimal, yet cozy accent furniture? This small, round pouf made of high quality fabric will be a perfect choice. Use it as a small useful ottoman, a stylish footstool or a modern side table for your living room or bedroom. A beautiful and functional addition to every interior.

description.title: Delivery
descriptions: Delivered directly to your home by trusted couriers like UPS, FedEx, or DHL, depending on your location
Delivery is free for orders above €100, with all costs, taxes, and customs fees covered by noo.ma
You can expect delivery in 2-4 business days within the EU and 3-8 business days for the UK, Switzerland, and Norway, starting from the dispatch date
All products from one order are being shipped together unless otherwise stated

features.title:
The Original Jean Jacket
Since 1967
features.description: Rediscover timeless style with the jacket that started it all. Crafted to perfection, this denim icon combines classic design with modern durability. Whether you're dressing up or down, it's the ultimate wardrobe staple—versatile, rugged, and effortlessly cool since 1967.

features.title:
Effortlessly Vintage:
Distressed for Style
features.description: Get that perfect broken-in look without the wait. Expertly distressed for an authentic vintage-inspired feel, this denim jacket delivers lived-in style with all the comfort and character of a well-loved favorite—straight off the rack.

specifications.description: Washed and faded like an old favorite, this trucker jacket made of cotton-blend denim features burnished hardware and a relaxed fit that layers easily when the temperatures drop.

features.title: A Vintage Revival
features.description: Inspired by the charm of a rare vintage shop find, this denim jacket brings retro vibes to your wardrobe with modern craftsmanship. Perfectly faded and artfully distressed, it’s a nostalgic classic reimagined for today.

specifications.description: We found this garment in a vintage shop and loved it so much that we decided to revive it for the 21st century. With supersoft 100% cotton jersey and a relaxed fit, this is the essential tee at its very finest.
